[SPEAKER_08]: I will do water sewer enterprise fund.

32
00:01:07,123 --> 00:01:10,646
[SPEAKER_08]: They will do library schools, and then we'll finish with debt service bonds.

33
00:01:10,946 --> 00:01:16,850
[SPEAKER_08]: So, um, for water and sewer, we have water Superintendent Dan Stone King and DPW Commissioner McIver.

34
00:01:17,550 --> 00:01:21,193
[SPEAKER_08]: Um and for the total request for the water sewer

35
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,901
[SPEAKER_08]: uh, to you both for our presentation.

36
00:01:30,921 --> 00:01:34,682
[SPEAKER_08]: I think that's just on.

37
00:01:37,642 --> 00:01:38,543
[SPEAKER_08]: Can you, is that working Shane?

38
