574
00:47:10,218 --> 00:47:10,918
[SPEAKER_12]: It's a new building.

575
00:47:11,359 --> 00:47:18,904
[SPEAKER_12]: It's an educational service for everybody in the community, for seniors, for people that come there to use the computers.

576
00:47:18,984 --> 00:47:21,606
