578
00:47:24,528 --> 00:47:26,630
[SPEAKER_12]: And there's podcasts going on, there's Makerspace.

579
00:47:27,731 --> 00:47:31,695
[SPEAKER_12]: This is the best thing that's come to the city in many years.

580
00:47:32,416 --> 00:47:36,299
[SPEAKER_12]: And like I say, I'm not going to sit here and watch it fall into disarray.

581
00:47:36,640 --> 00:47:41,264
