00:52:20,435 --> 00:52:27,538
[SPEAKER_07]: This is a critical position, you know, in my experience, and I've done my entire service, my entire career has been in government service.

643
00:52:27,758 --> 00:52:28,678
[SPEAKER_07]: And, you know,

644
00:52:29,914 --> 00:52:46,416
