[SPEAKER_07]: you know, there's charts for this kind of stuff.

653
00:53:56,873 --> 00:54:06,963
[SPEAKER_07]: So I don't know to what degree that applies to facilities, but these are the types of things that need to be taken into consideration and folded into capital planning, which is gonna be critically helpful.

654
