01:00:03,438 --> 01:00:04,038
[SPEAKER_06]: That would be great.

723
01:00:04,138 --> 01:00:04,899
[SPEAKER_06]: Thank you very much.

724
01:00:05,099 --> 01:00:05,979
[SPEAKER_06]: Thank you.

