755
01:02:09,373 --> 01:02:14,295
[SPEAKER_02]: They walk downtown and they buy food and drinks in Medford.

756
01:02:15,578 --> 01:02:16,639
[SPEAKER_02]: So, two things.

757
01:02:16,980 --> 01:02:21,144
[SPEAKER_02]: One, we love the river, but we also love the library.

758
01:02:21,805 --> 01:02:26,750
[SPEAKER_02]: If we don't fund the library and I can tell you half the time, the library doesn't have my books.

759
