810
01:06:13,559 --> 01:06:17,520
[SPEAKER_00]: But I would just like to make a few points this evening.

811
01:06:18,180 --> 01:06:22,322
[SPEAKER_00]: I know you've all mentioned this before, but one of the things that,

812
01:06:25,314 --> 01:06:43,382
