826
01:08:29,064 --> 01:08:31,865
[SPEAKER_00]: And I went into one of the rooms to sit to wait for Barbara.

827
01:08:31,885 --> 01:08:38,908
[SPEAKER_00]: And I wasn't paying attention exactly to my surroundings and there was a tap on the glass window.

828
01:08:39,608 --> 01:08:42,609
[SPEAKER_00]: And it was a woman in probably her middle 30s.

829
01:08:43,430 --> 01:08:48,452
[SPEAKER_00]: And she had taken a tablet from the kiosk that was just right there outside the door.

830
01:08:49,432 --> 01:08:50,833
[SPEAKER_00]: And she said, I've.

831
01:08:52,231 --> 01:08:55,014
[SPEAKER_00]: have this room assigned to me for the next hour.

832
01:08:55,474 --> 01:08:56,875
[SPEAKER_00]: And I apologized to her.

833
01:08:56,895 --> 01:08:57,816
[SPEAKER_00]: I said, I'm very sorry.

834
01:08:57,836 --> 01:08:58,877
[SPEAKER_00]: I was just sitting here.

835
01:08:59,458 --> 01:09:03,281
[SPEAKER_00]: And she said, no, she said, I'm having a job interview.

836
01:09:04,162 --> 01:09:05,963
[SPEAKER_00]: She came to the library.

837
01:09:06,364 --> 01:09:09,266
[SPEAKER_00]: She took a tablet from the library.

838
01:09:09,707 --> 01:09:14,331
[SPEAKER_00]: She went into a quiet space to take a job interview.

839
01:09:14,351 --> 01:09:15,892
[SPEAKER_00]: And I waited for her.

840
01:09:16,373 --> 01:09:19,696
[SPEAKER_00]: And when she was finished, she told me she did get the job.

841
01:09:20,316 --> 01:09:26,761
[SPEAKER_00]: So that's just a beautiful story to see what the library is doing for the citizens here in Medford.

842
01:09:27,382 --> 01:09:37,589
[SPEAKER_00]: And I fully understand that you all have the best interest of our library to continue to be funded and so forth.

843
01:09:37,670 --> 01:09:41,813
[SPEAKER_00]: But just that small story I told you this evening shows that

844
01:09:42,293 --> 01:09:51,360
[SPEAKER_00]: You know, there are so many ways this building has offered itself to the community, and I appreciate your time this evening.

845
01:09:51,500 --> 01:09:51,940
[SPEAKER_00]: Thank you.

